[h4 
	" Cancel long weapon effects (MMX3)
	$LF
	[a id=heading-22966 
	]a
]h4
[p 
	"If you use charged Gravity Well or Triad Thunder, you can cancel the long weapon effect by entering the sub-menu and exiting with a different weapon. This is useful when getting items that require those weapons, or when using Gravity Well against Blast Hornet (above).
	$LF
]p
[h4 
	" Lag glitches that can only be performed on consoles
	$LF
	[a id=heading-23273 
	]a
]h4
[p 
	"Because of the console's inferior power, often there is lag on consoles where there wouldn't
	$LF
	"be on a computer emulator. Though lag is usually undesirable, sometimes lag can cause glitches.
	$LF
	"In that case, sometimes these glitches can only be done on consoles that generate the necessary
	$LF
	"lag. Computer emulators may not emulate enough lag.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"As an example, it is possible to skip the Crystal Snail miniboss in X2 on a console
	$LF
	"by using a charged-up Silk Shot. Apparently, it cannot be done in Snes9x.
	$LF
	"It is demonstrated in the 
	[a class=extlink href=http://speeddemosarchive.com/mmx2.html rel=nofollow 
		"console speedrun of MMX2 at SDA
	]a
	".
	$LF
]p
