[p 
	"[
	[a id=1 
	]a
	[a href=#r1 
		"1
	]a
	"]
	" Confusingly, the first form is called either “Neo Sigma” or “Sigma”, and the second form is called either “Sigma Virus” or “Neo Sigma” (respectively). Technically, “Neo Sigma” is the correct name for 
	[em 
		"both
	]em
	" forms, but the wireframe Sigma will be called “Sigma Virus” on this page, because of the similar appearance to MMX3’s Sigma Virus.
	$LF
